---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Products" description="Kawasaki Ninja H2 dry sump kits and performance parts. Specialist components for the supercharged H2 platform.">
  
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
      <h1>Products</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Specialist performance parts for the Kawasaki Ninja H2 platform.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Product Intro -->
  <section class="product-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2>Kawasaki Ninja H2 <span class="text-green">Parts & Kits</span></h2>
        <p>The Kawasaki Ninja H2 and H2R represent the pinnacle of production motorcycle engineering – a supercharged inline-four producing up to 324bhp in track-only trim. For those pushing these machines to their limits, we supply specialist components including dry sump conversion kits.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Product -->
  <section class="featured-product">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="product-grid">
        <div class="product-image">
          <div class="image-placeholder">
            <span>H2 Dry Sump Kit</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product-content">
          <span class="product-category">Featured Product</span>
          <h2>Ninja H2/H2R Dry Sump Kit</h2>
          <p class="product-lead">Purpose-built oil system for serious track use and lightweight car conversions.</p>
          
          <p>The stock H2 wet sump system works well for motorcycle road use, but under sustained high-G loading in a car – whether on track or in a lightweight car conversion – oil surge can become a reliability concern. Our dry sump kit eliminates this issue entirely.</p>
          
          <div class="product-features">
            <h4>Key Benefits</h4>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Oil Control</strong> – Constant oil supply regardless of G-forces or attitude</li>
              <li><strong>Increased Vacuum</strong> – Reduced windage losses mean more power to the rear wheel</li>
              <li><strong>Reliability</strong> – Eliminates oil starvation risk under extreme conditions</li>
              <li><strong>Flexibility</strong> – External tank can be positioned to suit your installation</li>
              <li><strong>Simplicity</strong> – Fits in place of the standard water pump - an electric water pump is required.</li>            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="product-specs">
            <h4>Specifications</h4>
            <div class="specs-grid">
              <div class="spec">
                <span class="spec-label">Fitment</span>
                <span class="spec-value">2015- Ninja H2, H2R, H2 Carbon, SX and SE</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec">
                <span class="spec-label">Pump Type</span>
                <span class="spec-value">twin chamber design giving high oil evacuation rates</span>
              </div>
              <div class="spec">
                <span class="spec-label">Application</span>
                <span class="spec-value">Track / Race / Car Conversion</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="product-cta">
            <p>Contact us for pricing and availability. We can advise on installation and tank positioning for your specific application.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Enquire Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other Products -->
  <section class="other-products">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="stripe-accent"></span>
        <h2>Additional H2 Parts</h2>
        <p>We can source and supply a range of performance parts for the H2 platform.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="products-grid">
        <div class="product-card">
          <h3>Performance Parts</h3>
          <p>ECU tuning, exhaust systems, and engine components for the supercharged H2 motor. Contact us for specific requirements.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="product-link">Enquire →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="product-card">
          <h3>Cooling Upgrades</h3>
          <p>High-performance radiators and oil coolers for sustained track use. Essential for pushing the H2 to its limits.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="product-link">Enquire →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="product-card">
          <h3>Car Conversion Parts</h3>
          <p>Specialist components for mounting the H2 engine in lightweight cars. Adaptors, mounts, and integration components.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="product-link">Enquire →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About H2 -->
  <section class="about-h2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-content">
          <h2>The Ninja H2 Platform</h2>
          <p>The Kawasaki Ninja H2 is a supercharged hypersport motorcycle producing 200bhp in road trim and up to 310bhp in the track-only H2R variant. The H2R holds the record for the fastest production motorcycle available.</p>
          <p>The 998cc inline-four features Kawasaki's centrifugal supercharger – a piece of engineering developed across multiple divisions of the Kawasaki Heavy Industries group. The result is extraordinary power delivery with surprisingly linear throttle response.</p>
          <p>For car builders, the H2 engine offers an incredible power-to-weight ratio in a compact, reliable package. With the right supporting modifications – including dry sump conversion – it's an excellent choice for lightweight sports cars and specials.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">310</span>
            <span class="stat-unit">bhp</span>
            <span class="stat-label">H2R Maximum Power</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">998</span>
            <span class="stat-unit">cc</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Displacement</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-card">
            <span class="stat-number">240</span>
            <span class="stat-unit">mph</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Top Speed (H2R)</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Need H2 Parts?</h2>
        <p>Get in touch to discuss your requirements. We can advise on the right components for your application.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    padding: calc(80px + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.2);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Product Intro */
  .product-intro {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .intro-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .intro-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .intro-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* Featured Product */
  .featured-product {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .product-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .product-image {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    background: var(--tftr-dark);
    border: 2px dashed rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.3);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .product-category {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .product-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .product-lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .product-content > p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .product-features,
  .product-specs {
    background: var(--tftr-dark);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .product-features h4,
  .product-specs h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }

  .product-features ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .product-features li {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .product-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
  }

  .product-features li strong {
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .specs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .spec {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .spec-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--tftr-grey);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .spec-value {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .product-cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .product-cta p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* Other Products */
  .other-products {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .section-header p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .products-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .product-card {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(92, 184, 92, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .product-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .product-card p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .product-link {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
  }

  .product-link:hover {
    color: var(--tftr-green-light);
  }

  /* About H2 */
  .about-h2 {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--tftr-grey-light);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--tftr-dark);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--tftr-green);
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .stat-card .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-card .stat-unit {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--tftr-green);
    margin-left: 0.25rem;
  }

  .stat-card .stat-label {
    width: 100%;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--tftr-grey);
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--tftr-green-dark), var(--tftr-green));
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    color: var(--tftr-black);
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin: var(--space-sm) auto var(--space-md);
    max-width: 50ch;
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary {
    background: var(--tftr-black);
    color: var(--tftr-white);
  }

  .cta-content .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--tftr-darker);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .product-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .product-image {
      position: relative;
      top: 0;
    }

    .specs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .products-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-stats {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-card {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 150px;
    }
  }
</style>
